nodes.text: Shukut was the homeworld of the Mandalorian bounty hunter Ketsu Onyo.

Shukut was first mentioned in Star Wars canon in the 2018 reference book, Star Wars: Scum and Villainy: Case Files on the Galaxy's Most Notorious by Pablo Hidalgo. Shukut was first introduced in the Star Wars Legends 2009 reference book The Essential Atlas, co-written by Daniel Wallace and Jason Fry.
